Execute a system command

{{Task|Programming environment operations}}

;Task:
Run either the &nbsp; <tt><span class="rosetta__text--bold">ls</span></tt> &nbsp; system command &nbsp; (<tt><span class="rosetta__text--bold">dir</span></tt> &nbsp; on Windows), &nbsp; or the &nbsp; <tt><span class="rosetta__text--bold">pause</span></tt> &nbsp;  system command.
<br><br>
;Related tasks
* <a class="rosetta__link--rosetta" href="http://rosettacode.org/wiki/Get_system_command_output " title="Get_system_command_output "> Get system command output</a>
